Short: Handling of 0-dimension mappings
From: Lars
Date: 990310
Type: Feature
State: Acknowledged

There must be an easy way to add/remove keys from
0-dimension mappings. With that, order_alist() is no
longer necessary for lookup-the-key stuff.

m_add(m, key, data...) in addition to m + ([ ])
member(m, key) return 0 or 1.
